name: The Slums of Mega-City One
description: Mega-City One is a huge fictional post-nuclear megalopolis-size megacity city-state in the Judge Dredd comic book series and its spinoff series. It was one of three major areas to survive the nuclear war in 2070, due to an experimental laser missile-defense system built not long before. 3D concept art illustration. Created with: C4D, OctaneRender, Procreate, Photoshop Year: 2021
